---
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---
<Header />

<style>
  /* 0) Base */
  :root {
    --ink: #0D1A5A;
    --paper: #f6e4cc;
    --brand: #ef3741;
  }
  body {
    margin: 0; padding: 0; overflow-x: hidden;
    font-family: 'Gotham', sans-serif;
    color: var(--ink);
    background: var(--paper);
  }
  .services-wrapper * { box-sizing: border-box; font-family: 'Gotham', sans-serif; }

  /* 1) Page shell */
  .services-section { width: 100vw; background: var(--paper); }

  /* 2) Top title + intro (improved readability) */
  .services-section h1 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 8rem);
    color: var(--brand);
    margin: 5rem;
    padding: 4rem 1rem 1rem;
    line-height: 1.05;
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }
  .intro-text {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin: 0 auto 3rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.9;              /* ↑ readability */
    max-width: 1000px;             /* ↓ line length */
    padding: 0 2rem 4rem;
  }

  /* 3) Rows (balanced heights + readable text) */
  .row {
    display: flex; width: 100%; margin: 0; padding: 0;
    align-items: stretch;          /* keep columns equal vertically */
  }
  .left, .right { width: 50%; min-height: 380px; }

  .image {
    background: var(--ink);
    display: flex; align-items: stretch; justify-content: center;
  }
  .image picture, .image img {
    width: 100%; height: 100%;
  }
  .image img {
    object-fit: cover;             /* fills column */
    object-position: center;       /* adjust focal point if needed */
    display: block;
  }

  .text {
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    line-height: 1.9;              /* ↑ */
    padding: 3rem 2rem;
    text-align: left;              /* easier to read than centered */
    display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
  }
  .text .inner {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 720px;              /* control line length */
  }
  .bold-intro {
    display: block;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--brand);
    font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.2vw, 3rem);   /* ↑ hierarchy */
    line-height: 1.25;
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .spacer {
    height: 0.5rem; width: 80px; background: var(--brand);
    margin: 0.75rem 0 1.25rem; border-radius: 2px; /* subtle separator */
  }
  .text p { margin: 0 0 1rem; }
  .text ul { margin: 0.25rem 0 1.25rem 1.25rem; padding: 0; }
  .text li { margin: 0.35rem 0; }

  /* 4) CTA section (refined sizing; same background) */
  .cta-section {
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    text-align: center;
    padding: 4rem 2rem 6rem;
  }
  .cta-section h2 {
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 6vw, 4rem);    /* reduced from 8rem */
    color: var(--brand);
    margin: 0 0 2rem;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.01em;
  }
  .cta-section p {
    font-size: 1.125rem;
    margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
    color: var(--ink);
    line-height: 1.85;
    max-width: 840px;
    padding: 0 1.25rem;
  }
  .cta-button {
    background: var(--brand);
    color: var(--paper);
    font-weight: 700;
    font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 3.5vw, 2rem);
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 0.85rem 2rem;
    border-radius: 1px;
    transition: all 0.2s ease;
    border: 2px solid transparent;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .cta-button:hover {
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    border-color: var(--ink);
  }

  /* 5) Mobile adjustments (hierarchy + spacing) */
  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .row { flex-direction: column; }
    .left, .right { width: 100%; }
    .text { padding: 2rem 1.25rem; }
    .intro-text { padding: 0 1.25rem 3rem; }
  }
</style>

<div class="services-wrapper">
  <section class="services-section">
    <h1>SERVICES</h1>
    <p class="intro-text">
      We partner with ambitious startups to transform high-potential ideas into high-impact brands, strategically built,
      emotionally resonant, and globally scalable. From competitive analysis to creative execution, every step is designed
      to give your brand the edge it needs to lead. Below you'll find our process, from positioning and strategy to
      storytelling, identity design, and hands-on brand enablement.
    </p>

    <!-- Row 1 -->
    <div class="row">
      <div class="left image">
        <picture>
          <source srcset="/images/uploads/service1.jpg 1600w, /images/uploads/service1_1200.jpg 1200w, /images/uploads/service1_800.jpg 800w" sizes="(min-width: 1200px) 50vw, 100vw" />
          <img src="/images/uploads/service1.jpg" alt="Competitive landscape mapping and customer insight analysis during discovery" loading="lazy" />
        </picture>
      </div>
      <div class="right text">
        <div class="inner">
          <span class="bold-intro">First, we extract actionable intelligence.</span>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <p>Before any creative execution, we run a reconnaissance operation to decode your market landscape. We analyze
          competitors, audit customer psychology, and identify whitespace opportunities your brand can own.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Comparative analysis & customer behavior insights</li>
            <li>Positioning statements & audience segmentation frameworks</li>
            <li>Clear differentiation that's sustainable and relevant</li>
          </ul>
          <p>This stage removes guesswork and ensures the next steps align with market demand and audience behavior.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 2 -->
    <div class="row">
      <div class="left text">
        <div class="inner">
          <span class="bold-intro">Brand visibility without control is just noise.</span>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <p>Once your position is clear, we design a tactical communication strategy that builds brand equity while
          amplifying market presence. We define awareness objectives, launching, pivoting, or scaling, and map the right channels,
          cadence, and voice.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Media ecosystem planning & social media strategy</li>
            <li>Narrative consistency & tone-of-voice calibration</li>
            <li>Message hierarchy mapping tied to business objectives</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Every tactic is engineered for ROI, not just recognition. We shape perception so the market doesn't just see you, it understands you.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="right image">
        <picture>
          <source srcset="/images/uploads/service2.jpg 1600w, /images/uploads/service2_1200.jpg 1200w, /images/uploads/service2_800.jpg 800w" sizes="(min-width: 1200px) 50vw, 100vw" />
          <img src="/images/uploads/service2.jpg" alt="Planning the channel mix and messaging cadence for brand awareness" loading="lazy" />
        </picture>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 3 -->
    <div class="row">
      <div class="left image">
        <picture>
          <source srcset="/images/uploads/service3.jpg 1600w, /images/uploads/service3_1200.jpg 1200w, /images/uploads/service3_800.jpg 800w" sizes="(min-width: 1200px) 50vw, 100vw" />
          <img src="/images/uploads/service3.jpg" alt="Narrative strategy workshop aligning founder story with market psychology" loading="lazy" />
        </picture>
      </div>
      <div class="right text">
        <div class="inner">
          <span class="bold-intro">In the absence of a clear story, your product becomes negotiable.</span>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <p>We construct a brand narrative designed to endure. Your story won't just explain what you do, it will define how
          the world talks about you across moments and mediums.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Founder interviews & product context mapping</li>
            <li>Archetype-aligned narrative frameworks</li>
            <li>Messaging systems for decks, web, social, and investor materials</li>
          </ul>
          <p>The result is a scalable messaging system. No more improvisation, everyone communicates from the same playbook.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 4 -->
    <div class="row">
      <div class="left text">
        <div class="inner">
          <span class="bold-intro">Design isn't decoration,it's operational infrastructure.</span>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <p>We build the visual and verbal assets that form the face of your brand. Not just ''making things look good,'' but
          engineering identity systems that work across contexts.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Logo suites, typographic hierarchies, brand marks</li>
            <li>Tone-of-voice frameworks, photography direction, usage guidelines</li>
            <li>AI-assisted iteration when it accelerates quality and clarity</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Everything ships in a comprehensive brand book so teams and partners apply the brand consistently across digital,
          print, packaging, and motion, building equity with every impression.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="right image">
        <picture>
          <source srcset="/images/uploads/service4.jpg 1600w, /images/uploads/service4_1200.jpg 1200w, /images/uploads/service4_800.jpg 800w" sizes="(min-width: 1200px) 50vw, 100vw" />
          <img src="/images/uploads/service4.jpg" alt="Brand identity system guidelines across digital, print, and motion" loading="lazy" />
        </picture>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Row 5 -->
    <div class="row">
      <div class="left image">
        <picture>
          <source srcset="/images/uploads/service5.jpg 1600w, /images/uploads/service5_1200.jpg 1200w, /images/uploads/service5_800.jpg 800w" sizes="(min-width: 1200px) 50vw, 100vw" />
          <img src="/images/uploads/service5.jpg" alt="Team onboarding session to activate the brand across channels" loading="lazy" />
        </picture>
      </div>
      <div class="right text">
        <div class="inner">
          <span class="bold-intro">We don't leave after the handoff, we embed.</span>
          <div class="spacer"></div>
          <p>After delivery, we support activation so the system actually lives. We train teams, advise on web and packaging,
          and guide rollouts.</p>
          <ul>
            <li>Internal brand training & QA during launch phases</li>
            <li>Site and packaging audits with implementation guidance</li>
            <li>Introductions to trusted execution partners</li>
          </ul>
          <p>Our mission isn't file delivery, it's building brands that win. That takes more than a logo; it takes a long-term
          ally in your corner.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="cta-section">
    <h2>No Packages. Just Precision.</h2>
    <p>At DoubleDown, we don't push cookie-cutter packages or bloat your scope. We tailor every engagement to what your brand
    actually needs, nothing more, nothing less. Whether you're starting up or leveling up, we align strategy, creative, and
    execution to match your ambition.</p>
    <a href="/contact" class="cta-button">CONTACT US</a>
  </section>
</div>

<Footer />
